<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.3">
<l>puṇarkku mayaṉā maḻikku maraṉām</l>
<l>puṇartta taṉṉuntiyō ṭākattu maṉṉip</l>
<l>puṇartta tiravākit taṉmārvi ṟāṉcēr</l>
<l>puṇarppaṉ perumpuṇarp peṅkum pulaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is Aja who creates [and] Hara who destroys,</l>
<l>staying in his navel from where he created [them].</l>
<l>He brings together the great union of sense organs everywhere,</l>
<l>as she joins on his chest as Lakṣmī whom he brought together.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
